ygData.msgSnippet: 1. Gatorscale sleeves on Ancient Crocodile level 30 1/4 chance of dropping it 2. Lizardscale Cloak on Tae Ew Templar, CT level 30 (?) Less than 1110hp. Almost
ygData.messageBody:
1. Gatorscale sleeves on Ancient Crocodile level 30 1/4 chance of dropping
it
2. Lizardscale Cloak on Tae Ew Templar, CT level 30 (?) Less than 1110hp.
Almost sure chance of dropping it, unless you get the rubicite greaves from
it =)
3. Gatorscale Leggings on the same Ancient Crocodile 3/4 chance of dropping
it

Tae Ew Templar is 20 min spawn, but usually there is something else as
placeholder.
Ancient Crocodile is 2hr-6hr spawn, but you have to clear the 3 crocodiles
there to make it spawn

P.s Prexus server has killed Lord Nagafen. )

Mazy
Level 49 Wizard
Prexus
